{"tid":709340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世盃】日本人世界盃完場後球迷留低執垃圾 日本贏波兼贏人心 更感染敵隊球迷","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T06:03:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27b9201d8671d65ab16e138eba0753a26ee8e151","tid":709340,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180620/large/1529435131_0c87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180620%2Flarge%2F1529435131_0c87.jpg&h=fd660801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本球迷的公德心非常有名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180620/large/1529435128_b555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180620%2Flarge%2F1529435128_b555.jpg&h=c04e915f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本球迷於完場後齊齊執垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180620/large/1529435129_45c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180620%2Flarge%2F1529435129_45c1.jpg&h=08d169bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次更感染哥倫比亞球迷一齊執。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 日本人的公德心可謂世界聞名，而今次有再有新猷。話說周二世盃分組賽對哥倫比亞之後，入場的日本球迷親自執走自己製造的垃圾，更感染對方的哥倫比亞球迷，齊齊於球場執垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n日本球迷由上屆巴西世界盃開始，已經被傳媒他們會在比賽之後執走垃圾，而他們攜帶入場的藍色垃圾袋，成為了日本球迷的代表。今屆世界盃，日本球迷亦不例外再帶藍色垃圾袋入場，今次他們更感染在場的哥倫比亞球迷，大家一齊執走垃圾，日本今次實在是又贏比賽，又贏盡人心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cache.netease.com/photo/0005/2016-10-06/C2NR2RUH0B4C0005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cache.netease.com%2Fphoto%2F0005%2F2016-10-06%2FC2NR2RUH0B4C0005.jpg&h=130de355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">圖為支那國足球比賽後 的球場情況</span>"},{"pid":"3d5bc23179055e2862f8010935472398fe05edf8","tid":709340,"uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"睇完隔離post中國小龍蝦假新聞，到日本贏波連球迷都一樣高質有大將之風<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明點解我要係香港呢個就黎比大陸吞噬既地方出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過少少唔得既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5c0ad58d6e6c824ffc68a0e9fb1e1518af3b9b","tid":709340,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}